        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Hookshanks (a gnome) passes himself off as one of Lamm's Lambs at a glance. A PC actively studying the 'children' notices the imposter with a successful Perception check (DC 17) against his Deception. He uses this to set up a Sneak Attack or to slip away.</p>"
