        "description": {
          "value": "<p>If reduced to fewer than half his HP or clearly losing, Hookshanks throws down his kukri and talks. He knows everything about the fishery and Gaedren's routine <em>except</em> the location of Gaedren's private den (A14). A captured, cooperative Hookshanks can shortcut the rest of the dungeon.</p>"
